  <div id="text-content_26415788-a5a0-4760-b5d6-6994465ba128" class="text-block-content">
    <p>If enabled in your course, you can use Announcements Redesign to participate in course announcements.</p>
<p><strong>Note: </strong>If Announcements Redesign is not available in your course, it has not been enabled by your instructor.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-discussions" data-step-uuid="49cc71a5-3e6a-43ad-9523-c28e247741ab">
    <h2 id="open-discussions" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Announcements</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/004/595/072/original/71e25163-35bf-40ed-a3bd-b211ce300808.png" srcset="" alt="Open Announcements" height="230" width="154">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_cedf547a-2a51-41d0-8e68-374b838d6904" class="text-block-content">
    <p>To view class announcements, click the <strong>Announcements</strong> link in Course Navigation.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open-discussion" data-step-uuid="79ac08e2-3a91-4311-9ffc-fe7ad6e0aed7">
